---
// src/pages/about.astro
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="About Us"
description="Learn about Armstrong Drainage. We are a family-run, local drainage and plumbing team in Sevenoaks (TN15), trusted for honest pricing and 24/7 rapid response."
>
  <main>
    
    <section class="relative bg-[#1a1a1a] py-24 md:py-32 overflow-hidden">
      <div class="absolute inset-0 z-0 opacity-[0.03] pointer-events-none" 
           style="background-image: repeating-linear-gradient(-45deg, rgba(255, 193, 7, 1), rgba(255, 193, 7, 1) 1px, transparent 1px, transparent 20px);">
      </div>

      <div class="relative z-10 max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 text-center">
        <div class="inline-block px-4 py-1.5 rounded-full bg-brand-gold/10 border border-brand-gold/20 text-brand-gold font-bold text-sm tracking-wider mb-6">
          OUR STORY
        </div>
        <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-6xl font-extrabold text-white mb-6 tracking-tight drop-shadow-lg">
          More than just a <span class="text-brand-gold">business.</span>
        </h1>
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-300 max-w-2xl mx-auto font-light leading-relaxed">
          We are proudly based in Sevenoaks, dedicated to bringing honest, hardworking values and rapid solutions to the plumbing and drainage industry.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="absolute bottom-0 left-0 w-full overflow-hidden leading-none z-20 translate-y-[1px]">
        <svg class="relative block w-full h-[40px] md:h-[80px]" preserveAspectRatio="none" viewBox="0 0 1200 120" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
            <path fill="#fdfdfd" d="M321.39,56.44c58-10.79,114.16-30.13,172-41.86,82.39-16.72,168.19-17.73,250.45-.39C823.78,31,906.67,72,985.66,92.83c70.05,18.48,146.53,26.09,214.34,3V120H0V95.8C59.71,118.08,130.83,119.3,192.39,101.51,235.34,89.06,278.36,73.1,321.39,56.44Z"></path>
        </svg>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="py-20 bg-[#fdfdfd] relative">
      <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center">
        
        <div class="relative rounded-2xl overflow-hidden shadow-2xl border border-gray-100 group">
          <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1585704032915-c3400ca199e7?auto=format&fit=crop&q=80" alt="Armstrong Drainage Team" class="w-full h-auto object-cover transform group-hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-700" />
          
          <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-black/60 to-transparent"></div>
          
          <div class="absolute bottom-6 left-6 right-6">
            <p class="text-white font-bold text-xl drop-shadow-md">Based in Sevenoaks (TN15)</p>
            <p class="text-brand-gold font-medium">Covering the local area 24/7</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-extrabold text-brand-black mb-6">Built on hard work and reputation.</h2>
          <div class="w-20 h-1 bg-brand-gold mb-8 rounded"></div>
          
          <div class="space-y-6 text-gray-600 leading-relaxed text-lg">
            <p>
              When we started Armstrong Drainage, we noticed a massive gap in the market. People were tired of dealing with unreliable contractors, slow response times during emergencies, and temporary fixes that didn't solve the root cause of their drainage issues.
            </p>
            <p>
              We wanted to do things differently. We put our own name and reputation on the line with every single job. Whether we are unblocking a sink, deploying our heavy-duty tanker for flood water, or doing a full bathroom refurbishment, we treat your property with the exact same respect we would treat our own.
            </p>
            <p>
              Today, we are proud to offer a true round-the-clock service. With our motto, <strong class="text-gray-900 italic">"Armstrong's the name, drainage is the game,"</strong> you have total peace of mind knowing local experts are always ready to handle any scale of emergency.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="py-24 bg-white border-t border-gray-100">
      <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6">
        
        <div class="text-center mb-16">
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-extrabold text-brand-black mb-4">The Armstrong Difference</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-600 max-w-2xl mx-auto">This is what you can expect every time you call us out.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
          
          <div class="p-8 rounded-2xl bg-gray-50 border border-gray-100 text-center hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow duration-300 group">
            <div class="w-16 h-16 mx-auto bg-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center shadow-sm mb-6 group-hover:bg-brand-gold transition-colors duration-300 flex-shrink-0">
              <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-brand-black" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M14 10h4.764a2 2 0 011.789 2.894l-3.5 7A2 2 0 0115.263 21h-4.017c-.163 0-.326-.02-.485-.06L7 20m7-10V5a2 2 0 00-2-2h-.095c-.5 0-.905.405-.905.905 0 .714-.211 1.412-.608 2.006L7 11v9m7-10h-2M7 20H5a2 2 0 01-2-2v-6a2 2 0 012-2h2.514"></path></svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3">Honest Pricing</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm leading-relaxed">No hidden fees, no last-minute surprises. We provide transparent, upfront quotes for all our services and emergency callouts.</p>
          </div>

          <div class="p-8 rounded-2xl bg-gray-50 border border-gray-100 text-center hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow duration-300 group">
            <div class="w-16 h-16 mx-auto bg-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center shadow-sm mb-6 group-hover:bg-brand-gold transition-colors duration-300 flex-shrink-0">
              <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-brand-black" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 8v4l3 3m6-3a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"></path></svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3">24/7 Rapid Response</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm leading-relaxed">Drainage emergencies don't wait for business hours. Our specialized tankers and repair teams are on call 24 hours a day, 7 days a week.</p>
          </div>

          <div class="p-8 rounded-2xl bg-gray-50 border border-gray-100 text-center hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow duration-300 group">
            <div class="w-16 h-16 mx-auto bg-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center shadow-sm mb-6 group-hover:bg-brand-gold transition-colors duration-300 flex-shrink-0">
              <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-brand-black" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17.657 16.657L13.414 20.9a1.998 1.998 0 01-2.827 0l-4.244-4.243a8 8 0 1111.314 0z"></path><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M15 11a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0z"></path></svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3">Local Experts</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm leading-relaxed">When you hire us, you're hiring a dedicated local team. We care deeply about the Sevenoaks community and our local reputation.</p>
          </div>

        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  
    
  </main>
</Layout>